_sText:
A Zombie Escape map based on Half Life 1!

You enter the Gamma Complex of the Black Mesa Research Facility at the very time Gordon Freeman initiates the resonance cascade events. Enable teleports/generators and tons of other challenges, the final goal being to teleport yourself to safety (based on the HL1 sequences prior to Xen).

Original link: http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/128683.
Made a new one so people could see the update on the frontpage.
